man init

Normalde:
0 - shutdown
1 - single user mode (network,kullanıcı,parola yok. root a düşer)
2 - multiuser ama network file system yok
3 - multiuser text mode
5 - multiuser graphical mode
6 - reboot

Ubuntu:
0 - shutdown
1 - single user mode
2 - multiuser graphical mode
6 - reboot

